Package io.github.imunsmart.items

Class ProductionRecord

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.github.imunsmart.items.ProductionRecord
  • public class ProductionRecord
extends java.lang.Object
    ProductionRecord class, stores information about a production event, including the production number, product ID, serial number, date produced, and product (optional).
